metadata.name: SLUM QUEEN
metadata.description:
"Slum Queen" is a stunning art piece that celebrates the beauty and resilience of queens in the blockchain world. Created by Slumgods.eth using AI technology, this piece depicts a goddess-like figure with rich jewels and an elegant fur behind her crown. Inspired by Egyptian mythology, "Slum Queen" exudes grace and strength, representing the strength and resilience of all queens in the blockchain.

This art piece is dedicated to all the queens of the blockchain, paying tribute to their hard work and determination. Despite enduring pain and struggles, the "Slum Queen" glows with a glorious crown, symbolizing her triumphs and resilience. Whether you are a fan of art or simply appreciate the strength and beauty of queens, "Slum Queen" is sure to inspire and captivate you with its stunning depiction of resilience and grace.
